of HIV+ patient has become longer and this meant that he would start ageing. 
International literature demonstrated that the HIV+ patient is more fragile than 
any other person of the same age and that doesn't present the viral infection.
OBJECTIVE: design, development and test of a new web-based instrument to allow 
the self-administration of the new questionnaire SELFY MPI created during the 
