Multidisciplinary Integrated Metabolic Rehabilitation in Elderly Obese Patients: 
Effects on Cardiovascular Risk Factors, Fatigue and Muscle Performance.

Rigamonti AE(1), De Col A(2), Tamini S(3), Cicolini S(4), Caroli D(5), De 
